001package doctorwhoapp.backend.domain;
002
003import doctorwhoapp.backend.data.entities.DoctorEntity;
004import java.util.List;
005
006public class Companion extends Person {
007    private Species species;
008    private Planet homePlanet;
009    private List<DoctorEntity> doctors;
010
011    public Species getSpecies() {
012        return species;
013    }
014
015    public void setSpecies(final Species species) {
016        this.species = species;
017    }
018
019    public Planet getHomePlanet() {
020        return homePlanet;
021    }
022
023    public void setHomePlanet(final Planet homePlanet) {
024        this.homePlanet = homePlanet;
025    }
026
027    public List<DoctorEntity> getDoctors() {
028        return doctors;
029    }
030
031    public void setDoctors(final List<DoctorEntity> doctors) {
032        this.doctors = doctors;
033    }
034}
